data.description: Foreclosure Deadline is 12/28/2023. Need Buyer who can close Quickly. Strictly As-Is Sale. $95,000 in Price Drops and Price as been Bank Approved! We have inspections available to share. Please disregard moving boxes, Seller is in the process of moving. Amazing home on over an acre of land. Just pulling up to this home you’ll immediately know you’re in for a treat. This beautiful farmhouse style home is surrounded by mature trees and farmland. The immediate landscape is adorn with hedges and unique landscaping. Also you will find pavered paths, garden, shed, wood patio decking with gazebo and pond. The driveway is large enough for cars, boats and campers. Entering the home you are greeted with large foyer with coffered ceilings, hardwood floors and updated with recessed lighting. The Dinning room is big enough for most oversized tables and there are built-ins for formal dish ware. You also have a conveniently located powder room. The Kitchen contains all the space and items you need for the chef in you. A set of double glass doors leads directly outside to and area perfect for grilling. Also on the main level is a laundry room, a large bedroom and a full bath. The sprawling living room has cathedral ceilings, skylights, built-in speaker system and gas fireplace. Upstairs is the master-suite with cathedral ceiling, entertainment speakers and a luxury en-suite bath. There are two additional bedrooms and another full bath. It also has a new well pump and a new septic. This home is move-in ready so schedule your tour today and come see this amazing property! Love it or leave it with our 12-month ‘Buy it Back or Sell it for Free’ guarantee!* Do you have a home to sell? buy this home and we will buy yours for cash!* Schedule a tour right now! Buyer to pay short sale negotiation fee of $4,000 or 1.5% of the purchase price, whichever is greater, upon closing
